# {{ project_name }} - Coding Standards

## HTML

### Document Structure
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Page Title</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header></header>
    <main></main>
    <footer></footer>
</body>
</html>
```

### Formatting
- 2 or 4 space indentation (be consistent)
- Lowercase tag names
- Double quotes for attributes
- Self-closing tags: `<img />`, `<br />`

## CSS

{% if css_framework == 'vanilla' %}
### Property Order
```css
.element {
    /* Positioning */
    position: relative;
    top: 0;
    
    /* Display & Box Model */
    display: flex;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 1rem;
    margin: 0;
    
    /* Typography */
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-color);
    
    /* Visual */
    background: var(--bg-color);
    border-radius: 4px;
    
    /* Animation */
    transition: all 0.2s;
}
```
{% endif %}

### Units
- `rem` for font sizes
- `px` for borders and small details
- `%` or `vw/vh` for responsive widths
- Avoid `em` except for component-specific scaling

{% if use_css_variables %}
### CSS Variables
```css
:root {
    /* Colors */
    --primary-color: #2563eb;
    
    /* Spacing */
    --spacing-md: 1rem;
    
    /* Typography */
    --font-size-base: 1rem;
}
```
{% endif %}

## JavaScript

### Formatting
```javascript
// Use const by default
const data = [];

// Use let when reassignment needed
let count = 0;

// Arrow functions for callbacks
items.map(item => item.name);

// Template literals
const message = `Hello, ${name}!`;
```

### Functions
```javascript
/**
 * Function description
 * @param {string} name - Parameter description
 * @returns {Object} Return description
 */
function processData(name) {
    // Implementation
    return { name };
}
```

### Async/Await
```javascript
// Preferred
async function fetchData() {
    try {
        const response = await fetch(url);
        return await response.json();
    } catch (error) {
        console.error(error);
    }
}
```

## File Naming

- HTML: `kebab-case.html`
- CSS: `kebab-case.css`
- JavaScript: `camelCase.js` or `kebab-case.js`
- Images: `kebab-case.png`

